I get asked quite frequently &ldquo;Can I do $SomeTask with (DSC|Chef)&rdquo;. &nbsp;My answer is almost always a qualified &ldquo;yes&rdquo;.
Two Motivations When I get this question, very often there are two questions lying in the background. &nbsp;
 If I roll up my sleeves and dive into it, can I create automation for $SomeTask with (DSC|Chef)?The first question is pretty close to what was asked. &nbsp;The intent of this asker is to determine if there are hidden &ldquo;gotchas&rdquo; in automating a task with one of the configuration management platforms or if $TargetSoftware allows $SomeTask to be done in an automated fashion.

